{"tid":997782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"宮鬥劇教壞民眾！強國官媒批5罪狀全面禁播　《延禧攻略》被鍘","createTime":"2019-01-27T12:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T15:52:05.000Z","uid":13468,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85257c6e91904a0a2719a194c1d1851b4d5d80de","tid":997782,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"宮鬥劇教壞民眾！強國官媒批5罪狀全面禁播　《延禧攻略》被鍘<br />\n<br />\n宮鬥劇近年熱潮不減，《後宮甄嬛傳》、《延禧攻略》等劇皆締造驚人點閱率，但《北京日報》官方微博25日列舉宮鬥劇5大罪狀，並指出劇情中爾虞我詐、勾心鬥角、媚上欺下的劇情，與當前的社會主義、主流價值觀相衝突，據悉，中國各大衛視昨(26日)起已全面停播宮鬥劇。<br />\n <br />\n文章點出宮鬥劇的5大負面影響，包含追崇皇族生活、惡化當下社交生態、宣揚奢華享樂之風、弱化正面精神引導及美化帝王臣相，宮廷用語也影響民眾的日常言談，譬如「朕、臣妾、小主、本宮」等詞，一度成為時下流行語。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，中國自26日起恐難在電視上看到宮鬥劇，目前《如懿傳》已全面被停播，其他衛視在任何時段也禁播宮鬥劇，原本東方衛視下午時段播出《如懿傳》已被換檔，浙江衛視播出的《延禧攻略》也臨時被綜藝節目取代。（洪彩婷／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190127/1508350/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190127%2F1508350%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=6cLUeJot05wT1KwRYHvTdk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7d80a970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Frealtime%2F20190127%2F1508350%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_apple.realtimenews%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=ae00b8ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.entertainment.appledaily.com/realtime/20190127/1508350/?utm_campaign=twad_social_apple.realtimenews&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"9189aa1ab0fc22108abcc72b32cd2755b36d041b","tid":997782,"uid":62950,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">劇情中爾虞我詐、勾心鬥角、媚上欺下的劇情</code></p